headline: Molson Coors (TAP): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Molson Coors has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 9.3%. Its stock price has climbed to $60.94, representing a healthy 21.2% increase. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
